Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.97,0:00:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:01:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if... as if...\Nthis were a pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got trouble!\NPirate Krieg's underling...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a restaurant, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, do you have money for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.16,0:02:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Would a bullet do?\N--So you don't have money, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.67,0:02:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a good cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.67,0:02:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a good opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.41,0:02:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this place with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.61,0:02:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no longer needed\Nat this restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Strongest Pirate Fleet!\NCommodore Don Krieg"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you damn geezer!\NI'm the Sous Chef here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.36,0:02:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean you\Nno longer need me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You often get into\Ntrouble with customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You flare your nostrils\Nthe second you see a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even cook a decent meal,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you're dead weight\Nto this restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.31,0:03:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say that again...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the other cooks\Nsteer clear of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So go be a pirate or whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and just leave this restaurant already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.86,0:03:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I keep quiet, you just shoot your\Nmouth off, huh? You damn geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest I could overlook,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not just gonna\Nlet you trash my cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you say,\NI'll stay here as a cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's final!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what's the meaning of you\Ngrabbing the owner by the collar?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit screwing around...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard\Nyou try to kick me out,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:04:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll continue to work here as a cook...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...until you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't die! I'll live 100 more years!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That geezer is never short of words...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, you have permission!\NNow you can become a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to make up for it by serving\Nyou fruit macedonia, my princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, thank you! You're so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Any time...\N--And no apology to us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna sue you,\Nyou stupid love cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serving you tea, aren't I?\NThank me for that, long-nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You wanna fight?\NI won't go easy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat him up, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Please don't fight because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes, I'll stop.\N--Who said it was because of you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--By the way, you know...\N--Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The food you have here is delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it seems a little\Nexpensive for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it'll be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yours are not free.\N--Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too predictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you sitting around for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When customers sit down,\Nbring them moist hand-towels!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... with this and that going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,four days have passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When can we leave here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he really going to work here\Nas a chore boy for a year?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem? The food\Nis free and it's comfortable here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For you it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!\NLet's leave here soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a little longer.\NI'll try talking to Owner again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An hourglass...\Non each side of the skull...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to show the threat to enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That flag is... that flag is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake... it belongs\Nto the ruler of the East Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don Krieg!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... why are the Krieg Pirates here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see it, Patty?! They actually came!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna get rid of them, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Isn't it a mistake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Don of a pirate fleet with a\N5,000-pirate force we're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he come all the way here\Nto get revenge just for one of his men?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no mistake! He's really here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is not good!\NShouldn't we just get out of here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a huge galleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a huge ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Ghin came back\Nto repay you for your kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--H-Hey...\N--Wh-What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their ship sure is beat up...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like they\Nwere attacked by cannons...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, it's hard to think\Nthat damage is manmade.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they come across\Na tornado or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry... Can I have\Nsome water and food?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have money... tons of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even remember\Nthe last time I ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... give me some water and food...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He shows neither dignity nor force.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he really that Don Krieg,\NCommodore of the grand pirate fleet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don Krieg!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please! Help our captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really about to starve!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't eaten anything for days!\NHe'll die if he doesn't eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good! It's a riot to see
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the famous arch rogue\NDon Krieg like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have money this time.\NWe're customers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!\NHey, contact the Navy right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's at his weakest right now.\NThis is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to feed him anything.\NKeep him under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.47,0:10:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right! We don't know what\Nhe'll do once his energy's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's done bad things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He deserved to starve because\Nof everything he's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once he's back to normal, I bet he'll\Nattack this restaurant straight away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to give\Nhim even a glass of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I eat, I promise I'll leave quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please... help... me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don Krieg, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop begging!\NIt's not something you should do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't do\Nsomething so disgraceful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise... Please...\NI'll take leftovers or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.02,0:11:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! Are you trying\Nto gain our sympathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, out of my way, Patty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S... Sanji-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Ghin. Let him eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.01,0:12:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sanji! Take that food away now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize what kind of man he is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the man who's called\Nthe East Blue Ruler,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the foul player Krieg!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It started in a prison.\NHe pretended to be a marine soldier
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and took over a Navy ship by\Nkilling a senior officer on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how he declared himself a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.97,0:13:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sometimes raised the Navy\Nflag and entered into harbors
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to attack the\Ntowns and passenger ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.31,0:13:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He also raised a white flag\Nand then attacked enemy ships...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did anything to continue winning.\NThat's how he got to where he is now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh... so he plays dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His real strength is\Noverwhelming as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving after eating?\NThat's not possible with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Letting such a wicked fiend die\Nwithout help is for society's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S... Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th... This isn't what\Nwe agreed, Don Krieg!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you here under the condition\Nthat you wouldn't touch this restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that man saved our lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel alive again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey... Wh-What the hell\Nis going on in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see when we go in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! A-Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's almost no sign\Nof anyone on that ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a good restaurant.\NI'll take this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... that's what you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My ship became a wreck,\Nso I wanted a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get off this ship after you\Ntake care of what I tell you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don Krieg... This isn't\Nwhat you promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're about 100 of my\Nunderlings still alive on my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're weak with\Nhunger and severe injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, prepare 100 meals\Nand water for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're some who've\Nalready starved to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring them over immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.51,0:16:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling us to revive pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:16:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that are gonna attack this ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Refuse? Don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not placing an order.\NI'm giving you orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.29,0:17:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter who\Nyou are... don't defy me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sanji-san...\N--Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-san, I'm sorry...\NI didn't mean for this to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a bitch!\NLook what you've done!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Sanji! Where're you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the kitchen.\NI have to prepare 100 more meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.94,0:18:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sanji-san!\N--Sanji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. That's how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Krieg's spy, Sanji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let you go in the kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're fed up with your crazy behavior!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to stop me, go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.32,0:18:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's an incorrigible rogue...\NI know that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't matter to me.\NThat doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:19:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens after we feed them...\NIt's too much of a bother to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.27,0:19:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a cook. No more. No less.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's someone who's hungry,\NI'll feed him. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right for a cook to be\Nthat way, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Patty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, someone keep him restrained!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, you sometimes feed customers\NI drive away at the back door, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna say who's right,\Nbut this time, it's your mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to let you do\Nwhat you want any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect this restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.31,0:19:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, we have\Nonly one enemy to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's Don Krieg,\Nwhat can he do against us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a sea restaurant where\Npirates come and go every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're fully prepared to\Nserve any kind of customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:19:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you full now, Krieg-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.83,0:20:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the main course, how about...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a piece of iron dessert?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat Ball of Doom!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might've broken the doors.\NOwner's gonna yell at me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you did it to\Nprotect the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a small price to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you gonna do\Nabout those in Krieg's ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we'll spread butter\Non the ship and stir-fry it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll taste good, right? You lame cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you serve\Nsuch a nasty dessert?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the lousiest restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're damn annoying!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From all over his body...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullets...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.46,0:21:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't defy me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Steel arms more\Npowerful than anyone's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wootz steel-made body\Nthat is harder than anyone's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.37,0:21:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a diamond fist that\Ncan destroy anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.98,0:22:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have all sorts of built-in\Nweapons throughout my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 50-ship large fleet\Nand 5,000-pirate force!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.82,0:22:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've won all battles in the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.65,0:22:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the man fit to be called Don!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.99,0:22:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.33,0:22:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I tell you to prepare food,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.10,0:22:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all you have to do is\Nobediently follow orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.34,0:22:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't defy me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.34,0:22:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's probably enough\Nfor 100 meals in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.61,0:22:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it to your ship right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Owner Zeff!\N--Owner Zeff!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.35,0:22:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that, pops?\NI could've gotten hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.19,0:22:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z... Zeff?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:23:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I had\Na vision of a treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.28,0:23:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I always searched\Nfor that miraculous place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.22,0:23:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before someone else could\Nbeat me to it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the world is going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before I can even attain my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.41,0:23:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then take me to the time\Nwhen I knew nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.49,0:24:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that my memories won't fade
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.97,0:24:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay to give\NKrieg food like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.31,0:24:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Do something about that, pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.31,0:24:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.65,0:24:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What're you doing, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.32,0:24:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go picking a fight\Nwith Krieg, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.65,0:24:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds fun.\NGonna fight, Luffy? Need a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.66,0:24:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.99,0:24:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Protect Baratie!\NThe Great Pirate, Red Foot Zeff!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.99,0:24:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
